Contract CO2: addFlight()
Operation: addFlight(user: User, scanner: Scanner)
Cross References: User case: add a flight given admin status
Precondition:
  *The user is authenticated
  *The user is an administrator
  *scheduled and arrival time are unique to the airport
  *aircrafts are stationed at that the scheduled departure time
  *aircraft are available
  *flight number is unique
  *source and destination are different
  *source and destination are valid
Postcondition:
  *A new flight  is added to the flightCatalog, with all specified details
  *added a new flight that exactly matches the type selected by the user
  *flight's scheduled times have been integrated without causing any scheduling conflicts 
  *the new flight's number is confirmed to be unique
